                            From the start of the project, we provide accessible tools for your entire API lifecycle.
                        </p>
                        <button class="bg-black text-primary px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                            Get Started
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 bg-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center p-8">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>
                            <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>
                            <div class="relative bg-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 w-64">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                                    <div class="text-lg font-bold">POST/COM BE</div>
